name: Station Eleven
overview: A post apocalyptic saga spanning multiple timelines telling the stories of survivors of a devastating flu as they attempt to rebuild and reimagine the world anew while holding on to the best of what's been lost.

episodes.name: Wheel of Fire
episodes.overview: After renowned actor Arthur Leander tragically collapses onstage, Jeevan Chaudhary and young Kirsten Raymonde have a chance meeting – and soon face an important decision that could save their lives.

episodes.name: A Hawk from a Handsaw
episodes.overview: Twenty years later, Kirsten and her Shakespearean troupe, the Traveling Symphony, meet a mysterious man on their way to perform at St. Deborah-by-the-Water.

episodes.name: Hurricane
episodes.overview: While fighting for her only chance at survival, Miranda Carroll reflects on the cost of her relationships with Arthur and Dr. Eleven.

episodes.name: Rosencrantz and Guildenstern Aren’t Dead
episodes.overview: After Kirsten nudges the Traveling Symphony off-course to help unravel the mystery of the Prophet, a much grimmer truth is revealed.

episodes.name: The Severn City Airport
episodes.overview: After an unexpected landing in Severn City, Arthur’s ex-wife Elizabeth, son Tyler, and friend Clark confront an even more uncertain future.

episodes.name: Survival is Insufficient
episodes.overview: While Kirsten leaves the Traveling Symphony behind to track down the Prophet, the Conductor accepts an invitation for the rest of the grieving troupe that breaks her heart.

episodes.name: Goodbye My Damaged Home
episodes.overview: On a journey to unravel her deepest trauma, Kirsten goes back to the apartment she once shared with Jeevan and Frank.

episodes.name: Who’s There?
episodes.overview: Kirsten arrives in Severn City to rescue the Traveling Symphony - only to find herself trapped in a family conflict that began twenty years ago.

episodes.name: Dr. Chaudhary
episodes.overview: Jeevan and Kirsten survive their first winter alone until an argument sends Jeevan on an unexpected path.

episodes.name: Unbroken Circle
episodes.overview: Kirsten sets in motion her plan to free the Traveling Symphony, while Miranda tries to live the right life.
